title: The Kismet Cafe
description: California-style cafe and wellness supply store located at street level in Makati. Colorfully witty Ottoman-period-inspired wall murals and 1960's style decor plus Wi-Fi create an informal, relaxed atmosphere. Serves organic coffee, sandwiches with whole wheat bread--pressed, sealed, and toasted in a ''jaffle' press. Many organic ingredients used.
streetAddress: 5022 P. Burgos St, Barangay Poblacion, Makati City
